                                                <h1 class="title" id="page-title">Mentoring</h1>                        
                        <!-- #tabs -->
                                                    <div class="tabs">
                                                        </div>
                                                <!-- EOF: #tabs -->

                        
                        <!-- #action links -->
                                                <!-- EOF: #action links -->

                         
                          <div class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system clearfix">

    
  <div class="content">
    <article id="node-100" class="node node-mt-feature clearfix node-mt" about="/student-services/business-scholars/mentoring" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">
            <div class="node-main-content full-width clearfix">
            <header>
                  <span property="dc:title" content="Mentoring" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
              
       

    </header>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>Why is mentoring important? It helps people in a variety of ways. Below are some of the reasons<br />
mentoring is an invaluable tool for Business Scholars:</p>
<ul><li>Networking</li>
<li>Energizing</li>
<li>Renewed Commitment</li>
<li>Increased Learning</li>
<li>Increase Impact</li>
<li>Increased Self-esteem</li>
<li>Increase Skill Levels</li>
<li>Confidence</li>
</ul><p>
We offer mentoring for students in three areas</p>
<ul><li>
<p><strong>Professional through the Business Advisory Council (Application process) </strong></p>
<p>Learn from industry experts how to prepare for and succeed in the business world.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Faculty (Required) </strong></p>
<p>Learn from faculty members' experience and areas of research, giving insight into your own academic and career choices.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Peer</strong></p>
<p>Learn from another student how to navigate and succeed as a UIC Business Scholar.</p>
</li>
</ul><style>
